property.name: note
property.value:
All Footsteps are triggered by their markers, when the surface is detected in Unity it plays the One-Shots every 500ms. When sprinting each One-Shot is triggered every 300ms. Once sample is played the play head is sent to "End" to stop any unwanted footsteps played. Alternate footsteps are played for running on tile
To add variation to the footsteps each is a Multi Sound module with various different footstep recordings, to add further variation pitch and volume are modulated randomly.
All Footsteps recorded by Oliver Richardson
